    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Linguistics- Farci, Galic, French, Chinese, Russian

Name in the Garou Community "He who walks unseen"

Learning Rending and Aegis from Randal
Major Favor from Paris
One personalized weapon at crafts*5 (+1 trait over norm) from Alley.
Learn Animalism to Quell.
With wolf claws, a chunk of flesh and muscle tissue is literally ripped out of the target's body ripped out of the Kindred being Rended causing profuse bleeding.Damage: 1 additional Lethal, 1 Blood trait, 1 Temporary Physical trait as a CHUNK of flesh and muscle. Character can't heal it back for the rest of the night. But may heal it back the next day. 
Mechanics: Physical challenge - must declare at beginning of the challenge that wolf claws are out and player will be using the Rending. If the physical challenge is won, then the player has HIT the defender. Standard retests apply here. 1 Simple test for EACH hit - determines whether or not the player has succeeded in Rending the defender. There is no retest.]]>
    </notes>
