Major Pact - end OOC)

*Your Sire stands still silent, even after you sign*
*He hands you Sam - and escorts the two of you to the
door into the "real" world*
*He gently shoves you out*
*still in the Umbra, he speaks"
My last word to you?
*chuckling*
Goodbye

*all of the sudden you see around your Sire explode 
the fourth level of the Way of Fire*
*in mere moments you see your Sire turn into little
more than a pile of ash - and you feel the bonds you
had to him shatter*

*as you turn and walk away, the door into the Umbra
fades and vanishes*

*but still ... perhaps it is just your imagination ...
just barely on the wind, ever so faint ... is the
sound of your Sires chuckles*

End

