      <![CDATA[Linguistics (3) (English, Spanish, Hindi, Cantonese, Mandarin)
2 bentleys 2 black suvs

Buy 8+ acres of Real Estate north of Scottsdale/Phoenix and East of the I-17 near New River development for our good Giovanni friend at $740,000 total for two lots next to each other totally 8.78 acres total.  Purchase through Theo. H. Davies & Co. Ltd. a JM Holding company located in NY for quick transfer to whatever company/private interest Lorenzo Giovanni wants.

Purchase a mansion similar to my current one for a song at only $1,285,000 in East Litchfield Park (built 2007).  It features a courtyard with a two story wall and a large iron gate, plus all the fabulous amenities that young working ladies could want or expect in a new home.
Didnitas-3
Made Adel 12-14-08]]>
