    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Languages: Italian, Old Norse, Nahuatl, Zapotec, Klingon, Gaelic, Russian, Spanish, Latin, Cantonese, German, Yiddish, Enochian and Greek
Gangrel Secessionist as Mentor (6th Gen), Guiseppe Padovese from Concordia di Sagitaria Italy.
Thaumaturgy is from a Tzimisce with Thaumaturgy in clan.
Ritual: Chill of Oblivion, cast on Paulo every Wednesday unless otherwise noted.
Szlachta Modifications: 4 levels of Torso Armor, Vision Mod, misplaced heart (if damaged, must be repaired with Vicissitude, not healed with blood)
Beast Forms: WOLF - Quick, Lithe, Tireless, Attentive, and Alert (+Sharp): Enhanced Sense - Smell \ Taste
BAT - Alert x2, Attentive, Observant x2 (+Sharp): Enhanced Sense - Vision
Leap into the Shadowlands ritual bones are vicissitused into each of Paulo's index fingers.

Pathos: 10
Anarch Status- Well-connected, soldier, warrior]]>
    </notes>
