      <![CDATA[When in sword combat he adds... 
+6 traits for Martial Arts - Weapon style
+7 traits for Celerity 7 "Flower of Death" (costs 3 blood)
+3 traits for his Long Sword, +2 for his short
This gives a total of +16 traits for his primary hand and +15 for his secondary
All weapons are coated with 4 traits of "Scorpion's Touch" blood
4 lethal damage + 1 physical trait with his longsword, 2 lethal + 1 physical trait with his short
4 primary hand and 1 off-hand attack per turn
7 status on loan from various mid-west and canadian Princes]]>
    </notes>
