    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Gangrel Prestige- Mediator, Dangerously Mighty, Loyal
Camarilla Status: Acknowledged, Loyal, Feared
Anarch Rep: Champion x2, Committed, Hardcore x3, Honorable x2, Anarch Rep: Soldier, Veteran

Necklace: Ward versus Ghosts (Wraiths): given by the Tremere Chantry of Phoenix.

Gloves: Description: Black fingerless gloves.   Do one additional level of damage.  Gains 1 bonus ability of Brawl, gain negative trait: Violent.

Long bow, Cherry wood, Handmade (Gangrel Clan symbol carved into side): 
Bonus Traits: 6 Neg: Fragile, clumsy and heavy Spec. Abilities: Staking, armor piercing

Autographed copies of the Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Trilogy (all 5 books).

Soul Anchor Requirements:  Advanced levels of Thaumaturgy (It is an Advanced ritual), At least 2 levels of Path of Conjuration, 2 or more levels of wraith lore,  Necromancy ( or must have experienced Soul Stealing), talents of a medium (or ghost sight), and at least 4 levels of occult. By focusing through a jade talisman the powers of conjuration, and the knowledge of occult and wraith lore together,  you are able to make an anchor of sorts that will tie the soul into the body.  As long as the talisman stays with the body the soul is anchored and cannot be taken.  One level of aggravated damage is done as the soul tries to excape the body. Cost:  1 willpower & 1 blood trait from the subject, 15 blood traits from the Thaumaturgist, and 30 min to perform.

Talisman: + 3 physical traits (Quick)Add permanent neg trait: Lethargic.

Languages: Fish/Russian/French/German/Italian/Spanish/ Palawa Kani (One more language open)]]>
