    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Animal Forms - Fight: Black Jaguar (Bonus traits- Lithe, Quick, Wiry, Resilient, Sharp and  Observant) Sense: Hearing
Flight: Bat (Bonus traits- Alert x2, Observant x3) Sense: Vision

In combat in Jaguar form, bids 20 traits deals 3 agg plus poison and loss of 1 physical trait (quietus) per bite; 2 agg plus 1 physical trait per claw

Has 3 bites and 1 off-hand claw in Jaguar form

Obfuscate in bat form, bids 25 mental traits (13 +7 for bat, +5 for levels of Obfuscate)

Usually in bat form hiding in the prince's pocket in obfuscate or using Mask of 1000 faces to appear as an article of the prince's clothing. Will use cloak the gathering to hide the prince in times of trouble.]]>
    </notes>
  </vampire>
