  <item name="Bang Sticks" type="Equipment" subtype="Weapon" level="0" bonus="2" damage="Lethal" amount="1" conceal="Jacket" lastmodified="1/25/2004 8:47:53 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Bang Tip"/>
      <trait name="Hardened"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Clumsy"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Hardened: The polymer/magnesium alloy is capable of withstanding great stress and as such can be wielded with Potence without breaking.
Bang Tip:  On a declared shot, the tip of the stick strikes the target.  On a successful hit, this causes the shell to discharge, causing 4 levels of lethal damage ( 1(staff strike) + 2 (shotgun round) + 1 (mass trauma))]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Polymer coated magnesium alloy.  Can telescope from 12 inches to 3 feet and collapse back down again.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[The end of the stick has a small chamber that can be unscrewed to insert a shotgun shell.]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
