  <item name="Collar of Burning Eyes" type="Talisman" subtype="Enhancement" level="0" bonus="2" amount="0" lastmodified="1/25/2004 6:41:49 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[While worn, the caster's eyes take on the appearance of burning pools of blood, deep red in color with flickering flames deep in their core.  Flames and smoke occasionally seep out of the eyes.  Anyone within 5 feet of the Kindred smells something smoldering/burning and anyone standing directly in front of the Kindred does feel heat emanating from the eyes. (Though not enough to cause Rotschreck)  Similar to Gleam of the Red Eye, sunglasses can be worn to cover the effect.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Black leather collar with metal studs.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Game Effects:  While worn, the wearer gains the additional Social Traits: Intimidating x2.

Created by the Ravnos Justin Case using Horrid Reality, Perminancy, as well as Illusioncasting x5 and Crafts- Metalworking x2]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
