      <![CDATA[A finely crafted set of 20 red, leather-bound, enxyxlopedia style books.  On the cover is a stylized G.  Publisher is Giovanni University Project, Phoenix, AZ]]>
    </appearance>
  </item>
  <item name="Library: Occult" type="Equipment" subtype="Enhancement" level="0" bonus="0" amount="0" conceal="None" lastmodified="1/25/2004 7:15:46 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Ability Retest" note="Occult"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Occult" val="2" note="minimum"/>
      <trait name="Occult Library"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Gives Bonus traits to Occult retests and/or Lore of Knowledge based Abilities.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Some Kindred have accumulated vast stores of mystical knowledge over their many years. Such resources may have been inherited from a character’s sire, treasures gleaned from previous journeys, gifts from a mentor or even stolen from rivals. In fact, a library need not even be printed – books contained on CD-ROM or even a contact who knows occult lore may be considered a library for the purposes of this Background.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Per Blood Magic, Page 89

Bonuses on retests are based on the Level of Occult Library.]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
  <item name="Library: Ravnos" type="Equipment" subtype="Reference" level="5" bonus="0" amount="0" lastmodified="6/28/2003 3:30:22 PM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Unique" note="Justin Case"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Posession of this library grants the owner Clan Lore: Ravnos x5 (In-Clan)]]>
    </powers>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[(This library is all 
the research and information discovered in India, including the 
information from both Clanbook: Ravnos and Libellus 
Sanguinis:Thieves in the Night (Dark Ages Ravnos) and includes 
instruction/descriptions of the Ravnos disciplines)]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
  <item name="Library: Ravnos Lore" type="Equipment" subtype="Enhancement" level="0" bonus="5" amount="0" lastmodified="1/25/2004 6:48:58 AM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
