      <trait name="Unique" note="Justin Case"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Posession of this library grants the owner access to Ravnos Lore x5 (In-Clan)]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[10 CD set containing digitized documents found in India in both original language (Sanskrit/Urdu) and English translation.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[This library is all the research and information discovered in India per Clanbook: Ravnos 3rd Edition , including the information from both Clanbook: Ravnos and Libellus Sanguinis:Thieves in the Night (Dark Ages Ravnos) and includes instruction/descriptions of the Ravnos combination and Dark Ages disciplines)

Information authorized for OWBN use by R&U Coordinator Ben Russell on 10/17/2002]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
