  <item name="Shiva's Fire Snake" type="Magic Item" subtype="Animal" level="0" bonus="4" damage="Lethal" amount="1" conceal="Jacket" lastmodified="4/14/2007 8:57:58 PM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2">
      <trait name="Blood"/>
      <trait name="Willpower"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Incendiary"/>
      <trait name="Poison"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Short"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Unique"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Incendiary- Simple test to cause additional level of aggravated damage and target starts on fire.  Must spend 1 ACTION to put fire out.  Kindred must win a self-control test or go into Fire Frenzy. 
Poison- Simple test to cause additional level of aggravated damage to living creatures and additional aggravated every 20 minutes until she receives proper medical treatment.
Created by Shiva.  Owner must figure out how to control snake.
Traits- Quick, Sharp, Lithe, Resilient.
Very territorial  will attack anyone who comes in its territory.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[3 foot long Rattlesnake with full body tattoos.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Created by Shiva.  Owner must figure out how to control snake.
Traits- Quick, Sharp, Lithe, Resilient.
Very territorial  will attack anyone who comes in its territory.]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
  <item name="Shiva's Talisman" type="Talisman" subtype="Weapon" level="0" bonus="2" damage="Lethal" amount="2" conceal="Trenchcoat" lastmodified="11/19/2007 1:07:41 PM">
    <traitlist name="Tempers" abc="yes" display="2"/>
    <traitlist name="Abilities" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Staking"/>
      <trait name="Unbreakable"/>
    </traitlist>
    <traitlist name="Negatives" abc="yes" negative="yes" display="1"/>
    <traitlist name="Availability" abc="yes" display="1">
      <trait name="Unique"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[Shiva is considered 1 trait up on any Magical attack made against him, 2 traits up on any challenge with his Primary Path and 1 trait up when casting rituals.
If another person ever takes this item,they are considered three traits up in any Magical attack against Shiva.
Shiva always have an innate mental connection with your talisman, and can track it if moving at a normal walking pace. Shiva can always tell general direction and distance. Shiva knows if it is destroyed.
Wards vs Kindred and Infernal.]]>
    </powers>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[A  briar walking cane with a skull-like natural knob for hand grip.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Crated by ritual.  Made unbreakable by Paris Giovanni]]>
    </notes>
  </item>
