      <trait name="Unique"/>
    </traitlist>
    <powers>
      <![CDATA[If a person gets impaled on the spear, they can't get any closer to it's weilder.  Designed to hold the vampire in place while the rest of the crew kill him.
Traits vs breaking/bending 14 1 might retest.]]>
    </powers>
