  <location name="Falcon Field" type="Haven" level="0" owner="Justin Case" access="Private" securitytraits="7" securityretests="5" gauntlet="7" affinity="Protection" lastmodified="1/25/2004 9:21:17 AM">
    <traitlist name="Links" abc="yes" atomic="yes" display="5"/>
    <where>
      <![CDATA[4800 E Falcon Dr, Mesa, AZ 85215]]>
    </where>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Hanger Four:  Large T Hanger.  Listed as Chrysostom Enterprises.  Justin Primary Haven & Secondary Weapons Lab.  

Hanger located at end of runway.

Large storage room is reinforced and is used as one of Justin's Havens.  All Interior walls are considered to have 14 traits and 5 Health levels per 10 foot area for storage room alone.  All other walls and doors are standard.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Owner: Thomas Moore (Justin Alias) for airport.  For Hanger Four: John Chrysostom

http://www.cityofmesa.org/airport/default.asp]]>
    </notes>
  </location>
  <location name="Giovanni Castle" type="Haven" level="5" owner="Paris Giovanni" securitytraits="10" securityretests="5" gauntlet="2" affinity="Ghost" lastmodified="2/24/2008 2:59:42 AM">
