    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Castle was brought over from Itally brick by brick.  20' high wall around the grounds.Gate house must be passed through to enter.Large grounds that include a huge replica of the Hanging Gardens of Babylon, Lilith Temple area on grounds.  1st floor is public area, dining and sitting rooms as well as the library, kitchen, nurses room, and servant quarters, 2nd floor is bedrooms and security room.  3rd floor is one large room set up as Paris' meditation/tourture chamber.  Movable mirrors, lighting all controlled by remote that Paris has.]]>
    </notes>
