  <location name="The Armory" type="Business" level="0" owner="Justin Case" securitytraits="7" securityretests="2" gauntlet="7" affinity="War" lastmodified="1/25/2004 9:19:19 AM">
    <traitlist name="Links" abc="yes" atomic="yes" display="5"/>
    <where>
      <![CDATA[15001 N. Hayden Road Suite #110A, Scottsdale, Arizona

http://www.scottsdalegunclub.com/index.html]]>
    </where>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[The Scottsdale Gun Club (SGC) is located in the foothills of the beautiful McDowell Mountains of north Scottsdale, within minutes of both the Scottsdale airpark and the 101 Pima Freeway. Our facility is a free-standing building covering an area of over 30,000 square feet. Built in a comfortable Southwestern style, it houses a large, bright and well-appointed retail center, a multi-use Dojo workout area, with lockers and showers, plus the country's largest modern indoor ranges. SGC boasts 24 publicly accessible lanes plus 8 private shooting lanes and a luxurious lounge exclusively for Titanium members. In addition, SGC provides comfortable classrooms, meeting rooms and a unique large multi-story Tactical Shoot House™ - for tactical training of private citizens, law enforcement and military officials.]]>
    </appearance>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[Primarily Weapons Lab for Justin, also where police and espionage Influence Contacts contact Justin. 

Justin's "haven" in this location is located within the office area.

Gatherings held here are held in the Titanium Lounge. (closed to general public and non invited guests)]]>
    </notes>
  </location>
  <location name="Tremere Chantry" type="Haven" level="5" owner="Tremere Clan" access="Private" securitytraits="10" securityretests="5" gauntlet="3" affinity="Wisdom" lastmodified="11/19/2007 1:13:18 PM">
    <traitlist name="Links" abc="yes" atomic="yes" display="5"/>
    <where>
      <![CDATA[Queen Creek]]>
    </where>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[From outside appears to be an experimental orange orchard.
Starting about halfway in people who don't say the password get lost, eventually finding themselves walking out.  Some of the trees were once sentient/could move and many have been ghouled.  A few magical rabbits and hawks also inhabit the orchard.
Next is a dirt embankment.  Only entrance is a small 1 car wide road into building area. Just inside the embankment are Circles of Warding vs. Wraith, Fey, Infernal, and Garou.

There are several buildings inside the embankment that are connected by tunnels.]]>
    </appearance>
    <security>
      <![CDATA[Small radar station near by to detect incoming planes.
Tunnels do not necessicarily lead anywhere can be described as maze-like.
Motion detectors and lasers are on the top of the enbankment.
Encrypted phones inside the site, hard-wired only inside the Chantry.
Shiva's personal areas have Ritual of Darkness cast on them.]]>
    </security>
    <umbra>
      <![CDATA[Shadowlands- A dead Orchard
Dreaming and Umbra- Living Orchard.]]>
    </umbra>
  </location>
