  <location name="War Zone" type="Elysium" level="5" owner="Jimmy Collins" securitytraits="10" securityretests="0" gauntlet="3" affinity="War" totem="Puck" lastmodified="3/26/2004 10:32:32 PM">
    <traitlist name="Links" abc="yes" atomic="yes" display="5"/>
    <where>
      <![CDATA[East side of I-17 North of Dunlap, South of Peoria]]>
    </where>
    <appearance>
      <![CDATA[Large Concrete Industrial style structure.  Three stories high.  With angle opening as main entrance in one corner.  Inside is industrial themed.  Has scaring in the concrete walls and sheet metal and razor wire decorating the walls.  Across from the Entrance is a staircase leading up to an observation area known as the office.  The bar runs the entire length of the wall on the left.  The roof is three stroies up.]]>
    </appearance>
    <security>
      <![CDATA[Surveleince system in Office is tapped into security systems in the entire surrounding area to include private and public systems in a 1 mile rafius around the war zone.  There is a secrete back door leading out of the Office.  There is an emergency door in the rear of the building accessable to the public.  There is a hatch access to the roof which can be reached from the staircase outside the office but the decor camoflages the hatch.  There is a access in the rear alley to the sewer system which the NOS know about and Micheal Collins knows about, but nobody else knows.  There is a secrete basement accessable from the secrete door in the office.  The basement stores an emergency blood supply and a small weapons depot.

Bouncers are at least Brujah Ghouls and any other clanmates who deem kicking your ass nesassary.]]>
    </security>
    <umbra>
      <![CDATA[Ward vs. Garu in Office on all walls, ceiling, and floor.  All surfaces have been treated to rid them of shine.  Such as monitors and camera lenses.]]>
    </umbra>
    <notes>
      <![CDATA[War Zone has at least 100 blood traits stored in it at all times for the Brujah to use.]]>
    </notes>
  </location>
